Definition: a clause that used to be part of the contract with a professional athlete extending the contract for a year beyond its expiration
Example: the reserve clause was used to bind players to a particular ball club
Synonyms: article, contract, p, a, clause, that, used, to, be, part, of, the, with, professional, athlete, extending, for, year, beyond, its, expiration, reserve, was, bind, players, particular, ball, club
Category: noun.communication
